data.description: Beautiful updated 2 bedroom, 2 bath waterfront home with pool. Very spacious open floor plan with den/office area overlooking canal. Gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances and gas viking stove. Impact windows and doors throughout. New A/C.  1 carport and long driveway with plenty of room for parking. Salt water pool with large area for entertaining with tiki hut.  Utility room and separate storage room. New electric panel. New dock & pilings. South exposure!   Great location close to shopping, restaurants, golfing and the beach! Only one fixed bridge, federal highway.  Interior photos will be uploaded next week.
